\section{Conclusion}
  In the study, the bright soliton solutions and singular solutions for space-time fractional EW equation and modified EW equation are obtained by ansatz method. After reducing both equations to integer-ordered ordinary differential equations, the ${\operatorname{sech}}$ and ${\operatorname{csch}}$ type solutions are investigated. Substituting ansatzs into the integer-ordered ordinary differential equations, the nonzero coefficients in solutions are determined. The graphs of all solutions are depicted for suitable coefficients.
